data.description: Nestled in a peaceful well-established neighborhood, you will find this beautiful, efficient, and low-maintenance home. Boasting more than 1400 sqft of living space, this three-bedroom two-bath home is ideal for families and busy professionals alike. The expertly designed kitchen that features sleek granite countertops, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry perfect for creating enjoyable meals and hosting memorable gatherings.
